In 2015, Angel Gregorio, a Howard University alum, founded The Spice Suite, which quickly evolved into more than just a boutique for selling her own specialty spices. Fast forward a few years when Angel made history with "Black and Forth," DC's FIRST strip mall dedicated to Black-owned businesses! 👏🏾⁠
